snippet.title: Grokit - Official Winter Blast Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Grokit's Winter Blast update is available today, December 6, 2023. Get into the festive holiday spirit in this Grokit trailer, showcasing what you can expect with the latest update for the mixed reality social multiplayer hand-tracking party game.
